column2: This spreadsheet facilitates automatic tracking of when biomass samples are dry.  Created by Andrew Cunliffe (andrewmcunliffe@gmail.com)

column1: Please duplicate this spreadsheet for your use, and include it in your data submission

Enter values into yellow boxes only: (i) Investigator name, (ii) harvest site name, (iii) harvest date (YYYY-MM-DD), (iv) drying temperature, (iv) date / time [yyyy-mm-dd hh:mm], and (v) mass [g]. The Dry weight field should auto-populate once the drying conditions are met.

column6: Is sample dry? (verify weights were stable for ≥24 hrs before stopping!)
